shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021)
description: The Dunk Low 'Black White' also known as 'Panda' brings a classic two-tone look to its classic basketball construction. The shoe's low-top build emerges in leather, with a white base contrasted by black overlays, with further black on the Swoosh branding. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while underfoot, the two-tone look is matched by the tooling, which incorporates a concentric rubber outsole for traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (W)
description: A women's shoe, the Wmns Dunk Low 'Black White' also known as ‘Panda’ emerges with a classic two-tone look. Built entirely with leather, the shoe's upper sports a white base overlaid by black, with black also marking the Swoosh branding. Perforations on the toe box provide breathability, while white branding appears on the tongue and heel patch. Underfoot, the two-tone rubber cupsole includes a concentric outsole to provide traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (GS)
description: The Dunk Low GS 'Black White' brings a classic two-tone colorway to the basketball classic. A grade-school iteration of the shoe, the upper appears in a mix of black and white on its leather construction, with a lightly padded tongue for support. Underfoot, a white low-profile midsole gives way to a concentric black rubber outsole, which takes its traction pattern from the Air Jordan 1.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Grey Fog
description: Delivering a subtle two-tone colorway of the classic silhouette originally released in 1985 is the Nike Dunk Low 'Grey Fog'. The all-leather upper features a white base with contrasting overlays in a light grey shade. The Swoosh, laces, and woven Nike tongue tag are in the same neutral tone. Additional Nike branding is on the heel tab and padded sockliner. On the bottom is a standard rubber cupsole that pairs white sidewalls with a grey rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low White Gum
Nike SB Dunk Low Black Gum
Nike Dunk High Panda Black White (2021)
description: The Nike Dunk High 'Black White' also known as ‘Panda’ dresses the classic high-top in a monochromatic two-tone color palette. The iconic silhouette features a smooth white leather upper, set against black leather overlays. The toe box is perforated for breathability. The shoe rests on a rubber cupsole, with a concentric rubber outsole included for traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Red Swoosh Panda
Nike Dunk Low Phantom Metallic Gold (W)
Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Year of the Rabbit White Crimson Varsity Royal
Nike Dunk Low Next Nature White Black Panda (W)
description: Incorporating at least 20% recycled content by weight is the Nike women's Dunk Low Next Nature 'Panda.' The synthetic leather upper complements the clean white base with contrasting black overlays. Standard branding elements are featured, including a woven Nike tongue tag and an embroidered Nike wordmark on the heel tab. A pop of neon green finish appears on the sockliner and is accented in Nike's pinwheel logo. The low-top is built on a durable rubber cupsole with white sidewalls and a black rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Pro Why So Sad?
description: Scottish skateboarder John Rattray brings his commitment to mental health research and suicide prevention into shoe form with the Why So Sad? x Nike Dunk Low SB ‘The Predatory Bird.’ The bird graphic that inspired this low-top's name embellishes the lateral heel, while a lone question mark in yellow adorns the red suede heel tab. The leather upper in cheerful pastel blue and contrasting navy suede overlays has a Swoosh in Coastal Blue fading to Speed Yellow. The interior tongue tag features ‘Why So Sad?’ reflecting Rattray's crusade to bring issues of depression to light. The outsole in clear rubber provides grippiness whether in the bowl or on the street.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro PRM Valentine's Day (2023)
Nike Dunk High Panda (2021) (W)
description: The Wmns Dunk High 'Black White' brings a classic two-tone look to a classic high-top silhouette. Built with leather, the shoe's upper appears in a mix of black and white, contrasted only by the red on the woven tongue tag. The toe box is perforated to offer breathability, while the rubber cupsole anchors the build and maintains the black and white look. A concentric rubber outsole is included for traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low QS LeBron James Fruity Pebbles
description: King James' favorite cereal gets a cameo in the LeBron James x Fruity Pebbles x Nike Dunk Low. The laces and insole are decorated with multicolor flakes and the tongue is adorned with a Fruity Pebbles tag, which James himself has proclaimed as his favorite breakfast cereal. The bright yellow heel tab reveals a stitched LJ logo. Underfoot, comfort and traction are ensured by the clear white rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro QS Argon (2022)
description: The Dunk Low Retro QS 'Argon' returns true to form, first released exclusively in Japan back in 2001 as part of the CO.JP program. The upper is crafted entirely of leather, mixing two different shades of blue with a white Swoosh. Additional white details can be seen on the laces, back heel tab and the midsole, which features the traditional Dunk cupsole and traction pattern.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Miami Hurricanes
description: The Miami Hurricanes school colors inspire this Nike Dunk Low. Riding on the outsole in Gorge Green, the traditional cupsole features white sidewalls and a foam wedge for cushioning. The upper combines a base in Total Orange with overlays that contrast in Gorge Green, which repeats via the signature Swoosh, low-cut collar lining and heel tab. Nike branding marks the heel tab in orange stitching.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Concepts Orange Lobster
description: The Concepts x Nike Dunk Low SB ‘Orange Lobster’ updates this low-top classic as part of a longstanding collaboration with Harvard Square's oldest sneaker storefront. With lobsters as its inspiration, the sneaker is built on a nubuck upper in orange; the overlays have speckle patterning reminiscent of a lobster shell. The white tongue in breathable mesh and white-outlined orange Swoosh pair with the interior lining patterning resembling a lobster shack's requisite bib. Black sidewalls and rubber banding atop the toe box are nods to lobster claw bands. Traction is delivered via a rubber outsole in orange.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Montreal Bagel Sesame
description: The Nike Dunk Low Premium ‘Montreal Bagel Sesame’ features sesame-seed patterning on dark tan overlays with a lighter-tan leather upper in a playful design inspired by Montreal-style bagels. The Swoosh and heeltab with 'Nike' constrast in royal blue and the insole features wood floor imagery. Underfoot, the sneaker is finished off on a traditional cupsole in white and an outsole in gum rubber.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Rose Whisper (W)
description: The Wmns Dunk Low 'Rose Whisper' refreshes the classic style of the retro basketball shoe in a light-hearted hue. The sneaker's leather upper is constructed entirely from a white base complemented by Rose Whisper overlays and Nike Swoosh. A breathable nylon tongue provides comfort while the rubber outsole anchors the build.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk Low Sandy Bodecker
description: Honoring the legend behind Nike Skateboarding is the Nike Dunk Low SB ‘Sandy Bodecker,’ in a design inspired by and recreating the color scheme and build of the original and elusive eBay Dunk from 2003. The upper features patent-leather overlays in eBay’s ubiquitous colors intersected by clear cut-out panels that symbolize the original pair, which was destroyed at the ASR trade show in 2003. The interior of the shoe delivers photographs by James Arizumi which celebrate Sandy Bodecker’s legacy.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Peach Cream (W)
description: The Nike Women’s Dunk Low ‘Peach Cream’ arrives in a citrus colorway with heritage styling. The smooth leather upper in a pale grey pairs with vibrant orange overlays on the forefoot and heel. The perforated toe box ensures ventilation while support and traction are delivered via a traditional cupsole and a circle-patterned outsole. Subtle branding appears on the breathable nylon tongue in peach.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Teddy Bear (W)
colorway: Light Soft Pink/Pink Foam/Medium Soft Pink/Praline
description: Powder pink and fuzzy chenille distinguish the Nike Women’s Dunk Low ‘Pink Teddy Bear.’ The pink textile upper features overlays in matching suede and a cream leather Swoosh. The tongue and collar are delivered in a soft, comfortable velveteen. The signature Swoosh gets an unexpected detail with a lateral-side suede ‘Nike’ tag, while the medial heel is adorned with a teddy bear. Support and grip are supplied by the white outsole and gum rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (PS)
description: The Dunk Low PS 'Black White' is a grade-school shoe with a classic two-tone look. The vintage basketball shoe emerges with a leather construction on the upper, finished in a white base that's contrasted by black overlays, including on the Swoosh. A padded collar and nylon mesh tongue support the fit, while underfoot, the tooling maintains the black-and-white aesthetic to complete the look.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Next Nature White Mint (W)
description: Delivered in an understated pastel finish, the Nike women’s Dunk Low Next Nature 'White Mint' is an eco-friendly silhouette made with at least 20% recycled materials by weight. Against a crisp white base, the overlays at the heel and forefoot appear in a cool mint on the allover synthetic leather upper. Nike’s pinwheel logo indicating its commitment to sustainability appears on the sockliner in Nike’s signature Volt while the tongue tag and heel tab display traditional Nike branding.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro White Black Panda (2021) (TD)
description: A toddlers' shoe, the Dunk Low TD 'Black White' features a classic colorway. Built with leather, the shoe's upper sports a white base, overlaid by contrasting black throughout. More black marks the Swoosh branding, while a lightly padded nylon tongue supports the fit. The tooling continues the two-tone design, including a concentric rubber outsole that draws directly from the Air Jordan 1 for traction.

shoeName: Nike SB Dunk High Pawnshop Skate Co. Old Soul
Nike SB Dunk Low Adobe
Nike Dunk Low Arizona State
description: A heritage shoe is reimagined in the school colors of the Sun Devils with the Nike Dunk Low ‘Arizona State.’ With 'Nike' stitched on the heel tab and the signature Swoosh in University Gold, the smooth leather upper in Deep Maroon is paired with additional branding on the tongue tag and sockliner. Comfort and grip are delivered by the traditional cupsole and rubber outsole in amber.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Essential Paisley Pack Pink (W)
Nike Dunk Low Stencil Swoosh
Nike Dunk High Blue Chill
description: The Nike Dunk High ‘Blue Chill’ takes a heritage high top and treats it to a brilliant blue finish. The upper of smooth leather constrasts with overlays in a vivid pastel blue which repeats on the signature Swoosh, collar and rubber outsole. Adding pops of color to this two-tone palette are the heel table and Nike branding on the woven tongue tag and sockliner in Amarillo yellow.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low USC
description: With a color palette that recalls the original 'Be True to your School' series, the Nike Dunk Low 'Gym Red' showcases a simple two-tone color block. The all leather upper features a white base, with vivid red overlays. Contrasting gold hits appear on the woven tongue label, the Nike branding on the back heel and the sockliner. A crisp white midsole gives way to a red rubber outsole, with the same traction pattern as the 1985 original.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Mineral Slate Armory Navy
description: The Nike Dunk Low Premium ‘Armory Navy’ is delivered in muted shades of blue on a heritage favorite. The Mineral Slate upper in smooth leather features overlays in navy tumbled leather and is adorned with a matching signature Swoosh. The back tab, sockliner and tongue tag deliver additional branding salutes. Underfoot, a contrasting white midsole with a foam wedge for comfort rides on a rubber outsole in navy.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Reverse Brazil
description: Paying homage to the original 'Brazil' colorway from 2001, the Nike Dunk Low 'Reverse Brazil' inverts the bright green and yellow panels. The upper is crafted with leather, segmented with a two-tone block of Apple Green and Yellow Strike. Nike branding hits appear on the tongue and back heel, while a traditional cupsole with white sidewalls and green rubber outsole finish the look.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SP Kentucky (2020/2022)
description: The Dunk Low Retro SP 'Kentucky' released to celebrate 35 years of the silhouette. Drawing from Nike's Be True to Your School series from 1985, the shoe gives the nod to the University of Kentucky with a white and Varsity Royal colorway. Built with the leather, the upper is supported by a mesh tongue, while Zoom Air in the sockliner provides cushioning. A two-tone sole unit completes the look underfoot.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SE Lottery Pack Grey Fog
description: The Nike Dunk Low SE 'Lottery Pack - Grey Fog' draws inspiration from those who seek games of chance with the hope of winning big. The classic low-top basketball silhouette features an all-leather upper with a white base and grey overlays. A black Nike Swoosh highlights the upper but also makes subtle reference to a lottery scratch off as it displays small bursts of color. A grey rubber outsole secures the build of the sneaker while an interior foam wedge provides lightweight cushioning.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Coconut Milk (W)
Nike Dunk Low Active Fuchsia (GS)
Nike Dunk Low SE Lottery Pack Malachite Green
Nike Dunk Low Next Nature Phantom Gold Suede (W)
Nike Dunk Low UCLA
description: The Nike Dunk Low 'UCLA' takes inspiration from the Bruins color palette. A leather upper features a yellow base with blue overlays and Swoosh. A contrasting white midsole leads to a blue rubber outsole, identical to the original basketball specific tread from 1985.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Triple Pink (GS)
description: The Dunk Low GS 'Triple Pink' also known as 'Barbie' updates the traditional design of the vintage Nike basketball shoe. The sneaker goes against the traditional two-tone color blocking with an all-leather upper in light pink for both the base and overlays. Hot pink highlights Nike branding along the Swoosh, tongue tag, and heel. While the rubber outsole secures the build, a breathable nylon tongue gives comfort.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Medium Olive (W)
description: The Nike Women's Dunk Low 'Medium Olive' features a two tone color blocking reminscent of the 'Be True to Your School' iterations that were first seen in 1985. A white leather base blends with Medium Olive overlays, including the Swoosh and the back heel tab. A white midsole leads to an olive rubber outsole, with the traditional Dunk traction pattern crafted for the hardwood.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Retro Pure Platinum Blue Lightning
Nike Dunk Low Halloween (2022) (GS)
description: A legacy sneaker's '80s hardwood roots receives a spooky reboot with the 2022 Nike Dunk Low GS ‘Halloween.’ Underfoot, a comfortable fit is delivered by padding at the collar and a retro stitched rubber cupsole for comfortable play on the court or playground. The orange-and-white leather upper includes black details; in attendance is the trademark Swoosh and traditional 'Nike' on the tongue and the heel tab.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Valerian Blue
description: Color blocking in vibrant tones distinguishes the Nike Dunk Low ‘Valerian Blue.’ The heritage-inspired colorway features a white upper with perforated toe box and overlays in navy blue with a matching signature Swoosh. Hits of red appear on the back tab, sockliner and tongue tag with Nike branding. The traditional cupsole with white sidewalls provides support while the rubber outsole in navy ensures solid traction.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Safari Mix (W)
description: Utilizing a variety of different animal prints and vibrant colors, the women's Dunk Low SE 'Safari Mix' updates the lifestyle silhouette with a mismatched patchwork design. A white leather base is surrounded by safari and cheetah prints, along with mismatched colors on the lace area, pony hair and Swooshes on the left and right shoes. The Dunk Low is finished with a crisp white midsole and black rubber outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low Coconut Milk
description: A retro low-top gets a monochrome makeover with the Nike Dunk Low ‘Coconut Milk.’ Against a base of off-white, cream overlays pair with a signature Swoosh in crisp white. The tongue tag and back heel tab share branding details while comfort underfoot is ensured by a standard cupsole paired with white sidewalls atop a light-yellow outsole.

shoeName: Nike Dunk Low SE Fleece Pack Honeydew (W)
description: A fleecy build with overlays in honeydew green sets the Nike Women’s Dunk Low SE ‘Honeydew’ apart from more traditional Dunk iterations. The woolly fleece on the white-and-green upper is repeated on the inner lining for a cozy fit. The signature Swoosh, also in plushy fleece, is highlighted with darker-green stitching along its border. The tongue tag, heel and sockliner all deliver branding with a modern look. Underfoot, an outsole in honeydew green supports the traditional cupsole in rubber, echoing the original.
